Hexagram: 2 - ไท - K'un
Locus:
  Line: 4
Title: Receptive Service
---
The man observes the strictest self-restraint and reserve in dangerous
times. In this way he incurs neither injury from antagonists with designs
on pre-eminence nor obligations to others.
